org.nerd4j.csv.conf.mapping.ann

Annotation Type CSVFieldProcessor


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface CSVFieldProcessor
    Represents the processor able to perform the validations and conversions needed to translate a CSV column value into the related data model field and vice versa.

    Usage

    The CSVFieldProcessor annotation is intended to be used inside a CSVColumn annotation.

    This annotation is equivalent to the XML configuration csv:processor.

    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
